11. 📌 Tổng kết (cái bạn đang có)

Bạn hiện đã có:

✅ Strong domain model (exam system chuẩn hóa tốt)
✅ Clear backend pattern (RPC-first)
✅ Clean frontend architecture (App Router + SSR)
✅ Strict UI system (composition-based)
✅ Scalable folder structure (B3-ready)


******************************************************************************************************

Feature → UI needs → Component → Refactor → Reuse

feature bạn sẽ làm theo:

1. Skeleton (end-to-end chạy được)
2. Stabilize (chuẩn hóa UI + types)
3. Harden (refactor kiến trúc)

